(30408, 501117, 'http://www.baytree-cars.co.uk/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>With over 20 years experience in the motor trade, we are committed to offering great value to our customers, supplying quality vehicles at competitive prices. We strive to offer outstanding customer service and a second to none after sales service with a free courtesy car! All our vehicles are HPi checked and are fully serviced and prepared before delivery.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Open 362 days of the year</li>\r\n<li>Free courtesy car available</li>\r\n<li>Great after sales service</li>\r\n<li>Honest reliable help and advice</li>\r\n<li>After hours viewing always available</li>\r\n<li>Delivery service also available</li>\r\n<li>3 years warranty available upon request.</li>\r\n</ul>', NULL, '65/67 High Road, Moulton. Spalding. Lincolnshire. PE12 6PE', 'Welcome to Baytree Car Sales', '01406 373474', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439456558, 1441268848, NULL, 'https://plus.google.com/101819156259731879516/about?hl=en', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'baytree-car-sales', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30481, 501213, 'http://www.bexhillmotors.co.uk/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>With three branches two in Bexhill and one in Eastbourne we have an extensive range of up to 200 used cars &amp; commercial vehicles to choose from. We are confident that we can find the right vehicle for you.</p>\r\n<p>All our cars are PDI checked in our own modern workshops prior to collection &amp; all of our vehicles are HPI checked. Working closely with Santander and as licensed credit brokers we offer solutions to all your finance requirements.</p>\r\n<p>In addition we work closely with Customer Protect offering extended warranties for your total peace of mind. Part exchange is welcome and we would love the opportunity to quote for your car. We also buy cars for cash. Bexhill Motors benefits from it`s own fully equipped workshop staffed by highly experienced technicians in all makes. This gives Bexhill Motors the edge to offer superb customer service furthering our already excellent local reputation.</p>', NULL, 'Bexhill Motors Group, Terminus Road, Bexhill on Sea. East Sussex. TN39 3LR', 'Bexhill Motors is a family run business having over 35 years local experience in the motoring industry.', '01424222210', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1440063785, 1441182389, 'https://www.facebook.com/pages/Bexhill-Motors/171493159583357', 'https://plus.google.com/114962156712920781901/about?hl=en', 'https://twitter.com/BexhillMotors', NULL, NULL, 'bexhill-motors', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30412, 501128, 'http://www.northwooduk.com/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>Welcome to Northwood Eastbourne Estate and Lettings Agency, the place to go for hassle free renting, buying or selling. If you''re a prospective landlord, vendor, tenant or purchaser looking for a team of local experts who really care, then look no further!</p>\r\n<p>Our office in Eastbourne offers the unique Guaranteed Rent scheme for landlords looking for a true "let and forget" service. We also offer a range of options for landlords including, Tenant Find, Rent Collection, Fully Managed as well as our distinctive Guaranteed Rent scheme. If you have a property in the Eastbourne and surrounding areas within East Sussex areas contact us today.</p>\r\n<p>If you are looking to sell we listen and work with you to choose the right selling package that will get you the best possible price, in the fastest possible time and in the most efficient and stress-free manner, all at really competitive rates. We offer you packages which include professional photographs, floor plans and audio tours alongside continuous marketing through a number of internet portals, including Rightmove, to enhance your property particulars. With our teams'' knowledge of Eastbourne and surrounding areas within East Sussex we aim to provide you with a level of service that outweighs our competition. If you''re interested in arranging a free, no obligation market appraisal without the hard sell then contact our team on 01323 744 544 or Eastbourne@northwooduk.com.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, 'We are one of the leading providers of Guaranteed Rent in the UK. We do Sales, Lettings and Property Management', '01329829904', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439536208, 1439536735, 'https://www.facebook.com/NorthwoodUK', 'https://www.facebook.com/NorthwoodUK', 'https://www.facebook.com/NorthwoodUK', 'https://www.facebook.com/NorthwoodUK', NULL, 'northwood', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30387, 501094, 'http://www.thboler.com/contact-us', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>T.H. Boler is a company motivated by a lifelong passion and love for cars; passion is personal and satisfying your passion for cars is our ambition.&nbsp; Not just any car though: we specialise in European Luxury, Performance and Prestige Marques.&nbsp; Our state- of- the -art showroom is located in "F1 Valley" near Banbury and close to the historic heart of the British Motor Industry, convenient for access to London and the Midlands with excellent access to the UK''s motor and rail networks.</p>\r\n<p>We stock more than 50 prestige motor cars at any one time, however if we don''t have exactly what you are looking for our professional team will work with you to source it.&nbsp; T.H. Boler are not tied to any one manufacturer or brand, we are therefore in the enviable position of being able to offer completely impartial buying advice.&nbsp; This independent advice also means that you can be assured that we have the freedom to select only the very best quality cars of any marque.</p>\r\n<p>As well as sourcing your next car we can also offer assistance with financing your purchase.&nbsp; T.H. Boler are fully FCA registered giving us access to more than 35 different lenders who will help secure the best possible financing for our clients.</p>\r\n<p>Our commitment to service and the pride we have in our cars means that we operate an open-door policy.&nbsp; We want people to come and enjoy the T.H.Boler experience, to see and to touch the cars; the source of our passion, the fruits of our labour.</p>\r\n<p>Our test drive route has been chosen to make the most of some of the best driving roads in the country, on the route you will pass both the Land Rover and Aston Martin''s HQ''s as well as the National Motor Heritage Centre.</p>\r\n<p>So why not contact us today to start your journey of a lifetime in the car of your dreams?</p>', NULL, 'Banbury Road, Warmington Oxfordshire OX17 1JJ', 'Mercedes-Benz quality is synonymous with excellence and efficiency to vehicle buyers and drivers all over the world', '01295690933', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439367468, 1441114296, 'http://www.thboler.com/contact-us', NULL, 'http://www.thboler.com/contact-us', NULL, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5tOYQXJfFus', 'mercedes-benz-retail-group', 'uploads/usersite/30301_30400', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30416, 501133, 'http://www.brooklandgarage.com/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>We provide a helpful service to make sure that you are another satisfied customer. We carry a good selection of used cars in stock covering all makes and models. This ranges from small economical super minis &amp; hatchbacks with petrol or diesel engines, sports cars and luxury saloons, through to 4 Wheel Drive Off Road, SUV and Commercial Vehicles.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>We are based just outside of Rye, East Sussex, heading towards Romney Marsh, our Kent &nbsp;based garage is only small but holds a variety of different cars from petrol to diesel to sports cars and luxury saloons, through to 4 wheel drive off road, SUV and commercials&nbsp;to suit any of your needs and at various price ranges.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Our stock changes on a daily basis, so if you can''t see what you are looking for on our website then please contact us. We don''t want you to avoid missing out on our great deals. You can contact us&nbsp;by phone, email or by simply dropping in.</p>\r\n<p>Find our selction of quality used cars near the towns of Tenterden, Hythe, New Romney, Ashford and Rye.</p>', NULL, 'Pods Corner, Brookland, Romney Marsh. Kent.TN29 9RQ', 'At Brookland Garage near Rye, East Sussex between us, we have over sixty years of experience in the motor industry.', '01797342048', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439541227, 1441613566, 'https://www.facebook.com/pages/Brookland-Garage/136865553057484', 'https://plus.google.com/101141723002698099216/about?hl=en', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'brookland-garage-kent', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30430, 501152, 'www.churchroadgarage.co.uk', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>Church Road Garage for nearly new and used Ford car sales in the Surrey and Berkshire areas in the South of England.</p>\r\n<p>Church Road Garage has been established for well over 20 years in the Camberley, Ascot, Chobham, Surrey, Berkshire and London area and have succeeded in rapidly becoming the leading used Ford specialists in the Camberley, Ascot, Chobham, Surrey areas.</p>\r\n<p>We are a dedicated team that are at the forefront of supplying nearly new and older used Ford cars. Compare any of our prices against the new list price and you will be saving, you will be amazed at the savings!</p>\r\n<p>Every car is valeted and prepared to a high standard and as a majority of our stock is less than 12 months old you will have the security and peace of mind of the remaining Ford 36 month or 60,000 miles warranty that runs from its original date of registration.</p>\r\n<p>So if you want to buy your next car in a relaxed, no pressure environment from people who care about your needs and who are committed to providing that complete used car package - you''ve come to the right place!</p>\r\n<p>View all our used Ford cars in stock now</p>', NULL, 'Church Road Garage, Church Road. Windlesham. Surrey. GU20 6BH', 'Welcome to Church Road Garage, Used Ford Cars in Nr Camberley, Ascot, Chobham, Surrey & Berkshire', '01276451026', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439799665, 1441182751, 'https://www.facebook.com/pages/Church-Road-Garage-Windlesham/170942762953956', NULL, 'https://twitter.com/ChurchRoadGarag', NULL, NULL, 'church-road-garage', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30388, 501095, 'http://www.hastingscarsales.co.uk/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>Christchurch Car Sales in&nbsp;St.Leonards On Sea, Hastings, was originally Shirley motors started by my father Bob Shirley in 1961.&nbsp;I joined him in 1982 and we changed the name to what it is today.</p>\r\n<p>All our cars are sourced locally in Hastings, and we offer generous part exchange allowances.&nbsp;All cars over &pound;1500 come with a free 1 year&nbsp;SILVER PLUS comprehensive warranty.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>We are very proud to be the longest established used car sales in St.Leonards On Sea and&nbsp;Hastings and the surrounding area, and are now celebrating our 54rd year in business.</p>\r\n<p>We are the small showroom with the Big Reputation!</p>\r\n<p>Hope to see you soon, Will</p>', NULL, 'Silchester Road, St. Leonards-on-sea, East Sussex, TN38 0JB', 'Longest Established Used Car Sales in Hastings', '01424435956', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439367499, 1440147666, 'https://www.facebook.com/pages/Christchurch-Car-Sales/532361126813459', 'https://plus.google.com/u/0/108809700841429591824/posts', 'https://twitter.com/CCcarsales', NULL, NULL, 'christchurch-car-sales', 'uploads/usersite/30301_30400', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30437, 501159, 'http://www.chrispagekent.co.uk/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>For fantastic offers and great choice, Chris Page is your number one second hand car dealer with&nbsp; over 40 years experience. Based in Tenterden, Chris Page prides himself on offering a excellent range of quality used cars for every need. Phone anytime to arrange to view cars. Part exchanges considered.</p>', NULL, 'Chris Page, The Old School House, Smallhythe Road. Tenterden. Kent. TN30 7NB', 'Welcome to Chris Page, unbeatable deals on used cars in Tenterden, Kent.', '01580857097', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439801107, 1441182035, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'chris-page-cars', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30441, 501163, 'http://www.redhill-honda.co.uk/showroom/cars/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>Whether you''re looking for a new or used Honda car, you want to book a MOT or service, or you''d just like some more information about the Honda product range, Redhill Honda are here to help. Our friendly sales team will share all their Honda knowledge and our highly trained mechanics will keep your car running at its best. And with events, promotions and a lovely selection of biscuits, we''re sure you''ll want to come and visit us soon</p>\r\n<p>Originally the site that Redhill Honda is on was&nbsp;a Wheelwright &amp; Carriage Shop, with the Brighton road always being a busy transport link from London to Brighton. The site has always had the history of vehicle maintenance and continues to do so with Redhill Honda.<br /><br />Redhill Honda, though not the largest Honda dealership, has the extensive range and services that you would find in one.&nbsp;The friendly staff and relaxed environment make coming into our dealership hassle free and pleasurable.<br /><br />You can chat to one of our experienced sales people about our range of new&nbsp;and used vehicles, or relax in our customer lounge with a cup of tea or coffee while we take care of your car in our service and MOT departments.<br /><br />We like to go the extra mile so we can also provide free collection and delivery, free service wash and vacuum with your service and we have loan cars available on request.&nbsp;Everything is competitively priced from our cars to our servicing and parts.<br /><br />With your entire Honda requirements met, why go anywhere else?</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 'Redhill Honda, 105-115 Brighton Road, Redhill. Surrey. RH1 6PS', 'Welcome to Redhill Honda', '01737336039', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439802485, 1441183525, NULL, 'https://plus.google.com/109033426650873443062/about?hl=en', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'redhill-honda', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30482, 501214, 'http://www.southcroydonmotorcentre.co.uk/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>Welcome to quality, Reliability, Value for money and above all a safe quality used vehicle.</p>\r\n<p>You''ve found South Croydon Motor Centre, a family run Business where you will only receive the Highest level of service.</p>\r\n<p>We achieve high standards, meeting everyones needs from first time buyers onwards. All our cars are checked by Approved Technicians, Your car will receive a service and MOT unless previously discussed.</p>\r\n<p>We aim to be your first and only point of contact offering a service second to none.</p>\r\n<p>Thank you, Hugh Telford - Owner</p>', NULL, 'Highlea House, Golf Road, Kenley, Surrey, CR8 5ES', 'Welcome to South Croydon Motor Centre.', '02086603733', '07775773995', NULL, NULL, NULL, 1440063988, 1441615820, 'http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=', 'https://plus.google.com/share?url=', 'http://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=', NULL, NULL, 'south-croydon-motor-centre', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30396, 501102, 'http://www.westwaynissan.co.uk/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>As the UK&rsquo;s largest Nissan dealer group, you can look forward to a wide range of new Nissan vehicles and access to over 1000 quality used cars in group stock, from our highly reputable dealerships located around the country. Dedicated to offering the highest level of customer care in everything we do, we also offer our service customers a real time online booking system where you can check availability and book in your service or maintenance job in just a few simple steps.</p>\r\n<p>Not only that but we will provide our customers with a courtesy car and Free European Roadside Assistance when getting your Nissan serviced with us. We will also match any like-for-like quote from a competitor within a 10 mile radius, giving you peace of mind that you are getting the best possible deal. When you pre-book a test drive, we will ensure that we have the exact Nissan model waiting for you on-site when you arrive. This will allow you to get a good feel for the vehicle you are interested in, before you commit to making a purchase. At West Way Nissan we always have lots of special offers on our new cars and used cars, as well as a range of leasing, finance and business deals available. Browse our selection of new and used vehicles online or contact your nearest dealership for more information.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 'West Way Nissan Mill Hill, 517 Watford Way, London. NW7 2QR', 'Welcome to West Way Nissan.', '02037747454', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439368871, 1441182750, 'https://www.facebook.com/westwaynissan', 'https://plus.google.com/+westwaynissan/videos', 'https://twitter.com/westwaynissan', NULL, NULL, 'west-way-nissan-mill-hill', 'uploads/usersite/30301_30400', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30436, 501158, 'http://www.johnsons4x4.co.uk/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>Johnsons 4x4 Ltd are a specialist used Land Rover and commercial dealer based in West Sussex . We are proud to offer you a first class customer service and very competitive pricing, so please browse our stock list. At Johnsons 4x4 Ltd we stock a range of used 4x4''s and commercial vehicles to suit all budgets and lifestyles so we are sure to have the right vehicle for you.<br /><br />If you are looking for a second hand 4x4 or commercial vehicle in Horsham , then don''t delay, call us today to book a test drive. In order to offer vehicles to suit everyone we make sure that we update our stocklist regularly. It is therefore always worth giving us a call, even if you don''t see what you are looking for on our website.</p>', NULL, 'Rowhook Farm Bognor Road, Horsham, West Sussex, RH12 3PS', 'If you are looking for great savings on quality used Land Rover''s and commercial vehicles in the Horsham area , then you have reached the right place.', '01403453795', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439800834, 1439801546, 'https://www.facebook.com/pages/Johnsons-4x4/469996949805941', 'https://plus.google.com/u/0/b/108447365515127597216/dashboard/overview?hl=en', 'https://twitter.com/Johnsons4x4', NULL, NULL, 'johnsons-4x4', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30372, 501067, 'http://allautossussex.co.uk/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>Our recovery service is available 24 hours a day and is organised at your convince. We will travel far and wide to make sure that you are not left alone in your hour of need. We have a variety of different services available on site for recovery so please get in touch to find it more.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>It''s easy and fast and it''s FREE. To scrap your car simply complete the form on our scrappage page, press submit &amp; we will call you back to arrange a convenient time to collect your vehicle.</p>\r\n<p>Scrap Your Car Sussex remove hundreds of vehicles every year and we do so in a reliable, polite &amp; friendly manor - and above all in an environmentally friendly way. We are fully licensed by the Environmental Agency and have access to an ATF (Authorised Treatment Facility) in your area. All paperwork is filled in correctly (V5 Logbook) and registered with the DVLA.<br />Scrap Your Car Sussex covers the entire Sussex area for collection of your vehicle!<br />We also purchase vehicles for re-sale. If you have a vehicle to sell simply complete the form on the sell your car page, press submit &amp; we will give you a call back.</p>', NULL, '37 Brighton Road, Shoreham By Sea, West Sussex, BN43 6RE', NULL, '01273803516', '07950316516', NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439194755, 1440490769, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'all-autos-sussex', 'uploads/usersite/30301_30400', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30434, 501156, 'http://www.elitecarsuk.co.uk/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p class="justify">At Elite Cars we pride ourselves in presenting our cars to the highest of standards. We offer all main dealer facilities, without the inflated showroom prices. We endeavour to be the lowest priced used car sales centre, offering the best cars at the best prices.</p>\r\n<p class="justify">With over 20 years of experience in the motor trade you can be sure that we will be able to advise you on the many different aspects of a vehicle purchase whether you have seen a vehicle in our stock, want knowledge of model specifications, details of finance packages or if you know what you want and would like us to source your ideal car for you. As an independent dealer we can offer all this and more with a friendly and personal service.</p>\r\n<p class="justify">We offer various finance packages that we can tailor to your needs. All the finance packages are at the most competitive rates available.</p>\r\n<p class="justify">We specialise in 4x4&rsquo;s, 4x4 7 Seater&rsquo;s, MPV&rsquo;s, and People Carriers in both Diesel and Petrol forms. We also sell other types of cars from convertibles, sport coupe&rsquo;s, super cars, small hatchbacks, medium saloons to vans. Makes include &ndash; ASTON MARTIN, AUDI, BMW, BENTLEY, CHEVOLET, FORD, HONDA, HYUNDAI, JAGUAR, KIA, LAND ROVER, MAZDA, MERCEDES, MITSUBISHI, NISSAN, PEUGEOT, SKODA, SUBARU, SUZUKI, TOYOTA, VAUXHALL, VW AND VOLVO to name a few makes.</p>\r\n<p class="justify">Come and see us and we are confident you will appreciate our honest and customer service led environment.</p>', NULL, 'Market House, 2 Marlborough Road, Swindon, Wiltshire, SN3 1QY', 'Welcome to Elite Cars based in Swindon, Wiltshire. We are conveniently located just 5 minutes from junction 15 or 16 on the M4 Motorway.', '01793698498', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439800238, 1440147236, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'elite-cars', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30470, 501202, 'http://www.forcevans.co.uk/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>Customer service is very important to us and we pride ourselves on keeping our customers happy by offering a helpful friendly service and answering all of your questions with a smile. If you have any questions relating to our vans and services, call us today to find out how we can help you find your next second hand van. We always aim to exceed customer expectations, offering a wide choice of used vans</p>\r\n<p>At Force Vans we are renowned for providing premium used vans at outstanding prices. Many of the customers who have bought vans from us in the past return to buy their next used vehicle. Our team are experienced, trustworthy and professional.</p>\r\n<p>We are a Friendly family run business that specialise in former police vehicles and have 2 generations of motor vehicle experience we also sell ex NHS disabled access welfare vehicles and ex council and lease company vehicles we are a fully registered dealer that can offer you all the usual full dealer facilities such as finance p/x''s welcome delivery servicing mot and valeting service we also take credit and debit cards and can arrange shipping!</p>', NULL, 'Unit 5 , Beadle Trading Estate , Hithercroft Road , Wallingford, Oxfordshire, OX10 9EZ', 'Welcome to Force Vans, we are the leading and biggest ex police van dealer in the uk! We offer a wide range of used vehicles and all at competitive prices.', '01235510906', '07885970642', NULL, NULL, NULL, 1440059545, 1441614230, 'https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=http://www.forcevans.co.uk', 'https://plus.google.com/share?url=', 'http://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=', NULL, NULL, 'force-vans', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30439, 501161, 'www.gatwickcarsales.co.uk', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>Gatwick Car Sales started selling used cars in Lowfield Heath near Gatwick airport over 30 years ago and we''re still going strong! For a small independent company to last the test of time we must be doing something right and that is offering a personalised, friendly and helpful car sales lot without the pressure or bending of the truth you may recieve at other car dealerships. A lot of our customers buy used cars from us time and time again, safe in the knowledge that when they buy a car from us they get exactly what they pay for!</p>', NULL, '1-2 Church Road, Crawley, West Sussex, RH11 0PQ', 'Call us or pop in to view a vehicle if you have seen something you like and you will see why we are one of the longest standing used car dealers in Crawley.', '01293859994', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439801879, 1439802323, 'https://www.facebook.com/pages/Gatwick-Car-Sales/745021198846718', 'https://plus.google.com/b/116731018802396896674/116731018802396896674/about?hl=en', 'https://twitter.com/GatwickCarSales', NULL, NULL, 'gatwick-car-sales', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30472, 501204, 'http://www.hyundai.co.uk/dealer/brooklyn-motors-seaford', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>Based in Seaford and idealy situated to serve Lewes , Eastbourne , Pevensey , Hailsham , Newhaven , Peacehaven and all surounding areas for sales service and parts .</p>\r\n<p>As a friendly family buisines you can be sure of a warm welcome whenever you visit .</p>\r\n<p>make Brooklyn your number 1 choice for Hyundai&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 'Brooklyn Hyundai, Claremont Road, SEAFORD, East Sussex, BN25 2BA', 'Brooklyn Hyundai have been a main Hyundai dealer since 1989 which makes us the longest serving in Sussex .', '01323893040', '01323453176', NULL, NULL, NULL, 1440060386, 1440663975, 'https://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=http://www.hyundai.co.uk/dealer/brooklyn-motors-seaford', NULL, 'http://twitter.com/#!/Hyundai_UK', NULL, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sb07y7n6KkU', 'brooklyn-hyundai', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30443, 501166, 'http://www.gl51cars.co.uk/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>We offer quallity cars around Tewkesbury, Cheltenham, Gloucester,&nbsp;Gloucestershire Area,&nbsp;at very affordable prices. If you are after fantastic savings on your first car or looking to upgrade, you can be sure that you will find competitive prices and the best service from GL 51 Cars in Tewkesbury Cheltenham And Gloucestershire.</p>', NULL, 'Ledbury Road, The Oxhey, Bushley, Tewkesbury. Gloucestershire, GL20 6HP', 'Welcome forto Gl 51 Cars. car dealer based in Tewkesbury, Gloucestershire . Cheltenham, Gloucester', '01242681011', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439802679, 1439803047, 'https://www.facebook.com/gl51cars?ref=hl', 'https://plus.google.com/u/0/b/108387329437991881025/108387329437991881025/posts?hl=en', 'https://www.facebook.com/pages/GL51-Cars/1419070015014584', NULL, NULL, 'gl51-cars', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30393, 501100, 'http://www.westwaynissan.co.uk/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>As the UK&rsquo;s largest Nissan dealer group, you can look forward to a wide range of new Nissan vehicles and access to over 1000 quality used cars in group stock, from our highly reputable dealerships located around the country. Dedicated to offering the highest level of customer care in everything we do, we also offer our service customers a real time online booking system where you can check availability and book in your service or maintenance job in just a few simple steps.</p>\r\n<p>Not only that but we will provide our customers with a courtesy car and Free European Roadside Assistance when getting your Nissan serviced with us. We will also match any like-for-like quote from a competitor within a 10 mile radius, giving you peace of mind that you are getting the best possible deal. When you pre-book a test drive, we will ensure that we have the exact Nissan model waiting for you on-site when you arrive. This will allow you to get a good feel for the vehicle you are interested in, before you commit to making a purchase. At West Way Nissan we always have lots of special offers on our new cars and used cars, as well as a range of leasing, finance and business deals available. Browse our selection of new and used vehicles online or contact your nearest dealership for more information.</p>', NULL, 'West Way Nissan Hanwell, 117 Boston Road, Hanwell. London. W7 3SB', 'Welcome to West Way Nissan.', '02037747303', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439368457, 1441183165, 'https://www.facebook.com/westwaynissan', NULL, 'https://twitter.com/westwaynissan', NULL, NULL, 'west-way-nissan-hanwell', 'uploads/usersite/30301_30400', NULL, 0, NULL),
