(30392, 501099, 'http://www.economycars-hove.co.uk/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>The satisfaction of our customers is our main priority and so all our cars are sold with a full mot(where applicable ) and a parts and labour warranty,finance can be arranged and all major credit cards are taken.We are always pleased to see new customers and you are more than welcome to pop in for a chat, or just browse around.So next time you fancy changing your car have a look at ouronline showroom stock list and give us a ring on 01273 720359 you wont be disappointed.</p>', NULL, '57 Brunswick Street West, Hove, East Sussex, BN3 1EL', 'Economy cars has been selling used cars in the centre of Brighton & Hove for over 25 years,our policy has always been to sell quality cars at affordable prices.', '01273434349', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439368370, 1440493098, NULL, NULL, 'https://twitter.com/Economy_Cars', NULL, NULL, 'economy-cars', 'uploads/usersite/30301_30400', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30449, 501177, 'www.marklillydiesels.co.uk', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>At Mark Lilly you will find a pleasant no pressure showroom environment with sales staff that have been with us over 25 years hence creating long term relationships with their customers, this allows us an enviable reputation for customer repeat purchase.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>With such great staffing experience through all departments we really can offer what the customer wants.</p>\r\n<p>With our &ldquo;Buy with Confidence&rdquo; Award from East Sussex Trading Standards we hope you will feel even more comfortable to deal with us.</p>', NULL, 'Mark Lilly Diesels, Sunnybank Garage, Flimwell. East Sussex. TN5 7QR', 'Welcome To Mark Lilly', '01580879666', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439886034, 1441270038, NULL, 'https://plus.google.com/103566427154539317022/posts?hl=en', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'mark-lilly-garages-ltd', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30409, 501118, 'www.saxton4x4.com/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>Based in the city of Chelmsford, Essex, we are proud to be an official Overfinch and Onyx centre offering a diverse range of expertly modified 4x4s and specialist cars. Our state of the art showroom, the largest of its kind in the UK scaling over 100,000 square foot houses more than five hundred premium 4x4s over two floors all under cover, so whatever the weather you can view our vehicles all year round. You will find the most prestigious 4x4s handpicked from the likes of Land Rover, Porsche, Audi, BMW, Mercedes-Benz, Lexus, Volvo, Volkswagen and many more all under one roof.</p>\r\n<p>Browse our comprehensive line-up of models in our climate-controlled, mood-lit and relaxed environment with access to all areas provided by our bespoke fully-glazed scenic lift and expansive walkways. Take advantage of all the creature comforts on offer; such as our specialist coffee bar serving hot and cold refreshments to enjoy from our executive lounge and panoramic viewing area overlooking our boutique showroom. Families are also catered for through our specified children&rsquo;s play area fully stocked with games consoles, board games, and various books, so the kids can enjoy themselves while you hunt for your dream 4x4.</p>\r\n<p>Our multi-purpose site also features a sixteen-bay service paddock using the latest diagnostic equipment. Relax in our service reception offering a coffee bar and a viewing area to see all the work taking place by our fully-trained and experienced technicians. Every vehicle is professionally valeted and detailed by our expert team to ensure the highest finish on our vehicles. When your car is ready you can collect it from our designated handover bay from one of our knowledgeable Business Managers who are there at every stage to answer your questions. Find directions to our modern showroom on our contact us page or get in touch on to speak to one of our friendly team on 01245 351234 today.</p>', NULL, 'Westway Chelmsford Essex CM1 3BH', 'Saxton 4x4 is the UK’s number one independent 4x4 dealership having been trading in the world’s leading marques for over forty years.', '01245351234', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439456650, 1440492018, NULL, 'https://plus.google.com/100890867649789319382/videos?hl=en', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'saxton-4x4', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30407, 501116, 'http://www.taylors-pitstop.com/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>Based on the busy Balcombe Road on the borders of Surrey and West Sussex close to Gatwick Airport, the M25 and M23 motorways. Taylors Pitstop has a very large selection of quality cars at unbeatable prices. All our vehicles have undergone a rigorous 76 point check and have been HPI and Vehicle Mileage Checked to ensure your peace of mind. Taylors Pitstop specialise in arranging vehicle finance, car leasing, finance and car credit. This enables you to get the best options when finding and buying your car. In addition we provide Extended Warranty products, Tyre Insurance, Vehicle Replacement Insurance and full AA Breakdown cover.</p>', NULL, 'Black Corner, Balcombe Road, Horley, Surrey, RH6 9SP', 'Welcome to Taylors Pitstop, one of the largest independent used car Specialists in Surrey and West Sussex.', '01293859575', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439456391, 1440663856, 'https://www.facebook.com/taylorspitstopbalcomberoad', 'https://plus.google.com/+taylorspitstop/posts', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'taylors-pitstop', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30420, 501137, 'users.autoexposure.co.uk/caralot', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>We supply quality vehicles to the general public, with the benefit of over 20 years experience in the motor trade. Our aim is to offer the ''most enjoyable car buying experience you''ll ever have'' and our extensive experience previously running major franchise dealerships including Mercedes Benz and Volkswagen means we are best placed to offer this type of experience.</p>\r\n<p>We have up to 100 carefully selected and researched vehicles on display, and offer all the services you would expect from a main dealer including -</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Part Exchange</li>\r\n<li>Competitive Financing</li>\r\n<li>Extended Warranties</li>\r\n<li>Multi Point Vehicle Inspections</li>\r\n<li>Hpi and History Checks for all Vehicles</li>\r\n<li>Nationwide Delivery Service Available</li>\r\n</ul>', NULL, 'Unit 3, Canal Gate Park, Nottingham Road. Derby. Derbyshire. DE21 7SN', 'Welcome to Caralot. We are a used car dealership based in Spondon on the outskirts of Derby', '01332672444', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439542460, 1441182573, 'https://www.facebook.com/caralot', 'https://plus.google.com/109268198748164368448/videos?hl=en', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'caralot', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30469, 501201, 'http://www.alljapanesemotors.com/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>Why buy a car from Japan?</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Excellent high specification exciting models that are not otherwise available in the UK.</li>\r\n<li>Superior condition than the UK equivalent of the same age.</li>\r\n<li>No salt is used on the roads in Japan leaving the chassis (underneath of the car) corrosion (rust) free</li>\r\n<li>In Japan they have a very strict test every 2 years equivalent to a worthiness certificate that can cost up to &pound; 2000 a time.</li>\r\n<li>The Japanese take pride in their vehicles and invariably keep them in good condition not only for their respect for their vehicles but in anticipation for the test.</li>\r\n</ul>', NULL, 'KV Cars Ltd, 1 Rooth Street, Stockport. SK4 1DJ', 'Welcome to All Japanese Motors. The Japanese vehicle import specialists for over 13 years.', '01614807559', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1440059284, 1440663401, NULL, 'https://plus.google.com/109105000473105495084/about?hl=en', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'all-japanese-motors', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
