(30417, 501134, 'http://www.lighthousecarcentre.co.uk/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>Established in 1989, Lighthouse Car Centre based in Shoreham by sea, West Sussex, England is a family owned and run business that is very proud of the high level of customer care that our 1000''s of happy customers past, present and future enjoy (Why not have a look at our customer feedback page!!). Lighthouse Car Centre is easy to find on the A259 close to Brighton &amp; Worthing, please go to our contact page and click in the Map icon for directions. You can drive in and park on site.</p>', NULL, '116-122 Brighton Rd Shoreham by Sea West Sussex BN43 6RH', 'Welcome to Lighthouse Car Centre\r\nUsed cars for sale in Shoreham by sea (Brighton), west sussex', '01273596959', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439541379, 1440493304, NULL, 'https://plus.google.com/116662627400311134020/posts?hl=en', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'lighthouse-car-centre', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30458, 501186, 'www.lmcmotorsales.co.uk', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>Our sales staff have over 80 years of experience in the motoring industry &amp; always provide a friendly and professional service whilst maintaining excellent customer focus.</p>\r\n<p>We stock over 120 vehicles so you are sure to find exactly what you are looking for, whether that is a hatchback, diesel, MPV, sports car, classic cars and even Vans.</p>\r\n<p>To maintain customer service we have teamed up with Customer Protect to offer a warranty package to give you peace of mind.</p>\r\n<p>To make things even easier we may be able to provide finance packages to suit your budget. Part exchanges are welcome &amp; and we also buy cars for cash. Our friendly staff are always on hand to help so come visit us today.</p>', NULL, 'Lottbridge Motoring Centre, Lottbridge Drove, Eastbourne. East Sussex. BN23 6PJ', 'Lottbridge Motoring Centre LTD is a family run business that has been trading for 20 years in Eastbourne, supplying quality used vehicles at affordable prices.', '01323643326', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439889578, 1441270060, 'https://www.facebook.com/pages/Lottbridge-Motoring-Centre/287216114713376', 'https://plus.google.com/106443337075744398636/about?hl=en', 'https://twitter.com/LMCEastbourne', NULL, NULL, 'lottbridge-motoring-centre', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30474, 501206, 'http://www.bilbos.com', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>At Bilbo''s we pride ourselves on quality campervan conversions on the Volkswagen T5 base vehicle and have been manufacturing as a family business for over 30 years.</p>\r\n<p>Our range of VW camper vans consists of 4 different layouts: the New Space, T5 Komba, T5 Celex, T5 Nexa and the T5 Lezan.</p>\r\n<p>With combinations of long and short wheelbase elevating or hightop roof a variety of layouts is available to you.</p>', NULL, 'Eastbourne Road, South Godstone, Surrey, UK RH9 8JQ', 'Welcome to Bilbo''s the UK''s leading Volkswagen T5 conversion manufacturer.', '01342892499', '01342893793', NULL, NULL, NULL, 1440061218, 1440664235, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'bilbos-motorhomes', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30374, 501069, 'http://www.trojancars.co.uk/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>With nearly 30 years of new and used car experience in the Portsmouth area we are able to source high quality used vehicles presented to the highest standards. All of our vehicles and items for sale are hand-picked and offered at very keen prices. How do we achieve this? Our knowledge of the market, trade contacts and use of the internet means we can pass on our savings in the form of very competitive prices.<br /><br />We also specialise in classic cars, motorcycles and scooters, primarily 1950&rsquo;s and 1960&rsquo;s English and American; and especially classic British &lsquo;Rock &amp; Roll&rsquo; cars! Plus, we are always on the look out for interesting collectibles, especially motoring memorabilia, toys, jukeboxes and other items of interest.<br /><br />Please browse our pages and contact us by telephone or e-mail if you would like to discuss any of the items on display, or have similar items that you think we might be interested to buy.<br /><br />We are always looking to purchase or part exchange similar quality vehicles or items with cash either way.<br /><br />Please contact us to arrange viewing.<br /><br />Thank you</p>', NULL, '245–247 Francis Avenue, Southsea. Hampshire. PO4 0AL', 'Trojan Cars specialise cheap used cars | Finance | Warranty | Portsmouth and Portsmouth and Southsea Hampshire UK in pre-owned family, sports and prestige autom', '02392299080', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439195585, 1440492785, 'https://www.facebook.com/TrojanCars?sk=app_175456335854933', 'https://plus.google.com/112766815547566255020/videos?hl=en', 'https://twitter.com/TrojanCars', NULL, NULL, 'trojan-car-sales', 'uploads/usersite/30301_30400', NULL, 0, NULL);
