(30400, 501109, 'http://www.abbottcarsales.co.uk/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>Based in Peacehaven, Brighton we are a family run business that has been trading for 20 years and can boast a wealth of experience in supplying used cars, vans and ex Motability cars to the public of Sussex and the rest of the UK. All of our vehicles are personally selected for our forecourt and fully prepared to the highest standards by ourselves in house. Each vehicle is Hpi verified, comes with a RAC warranty with low rate finance available.</p>\r\n<p>Martin, Max and the rest of the team take great pride in the good reputation that we have in and around the Brighton area, this has been achieved by only supplying high quality vehicles with unrivalled customer service. This is something we strive very hard to achieve. When looking for a used car and van dealer in Brighton, then look no further than Abbott and Sons Car and Commercials sales!</p>', NULL, 'Abbott & Sons Car and Commercial Sales, 330 - 336 South Coast Road, Peacehaven. East Sussex. BN10 7EN', 'Welcome to Abbott & Sons Car and Commercial Sales.', '01273588884', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439454184, 1441183419, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'abbott-sons-car-and-commercial-sales', 'uploads/usersite/30301_30400', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30414, 501131, 'http://www.usedcarsleicester.co.uk/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>If you are looking for great savings on quality used cars in the Leicester area, then you have reached the right place. Braunstone Crossroads Motor Company are a specialist used car dealer based in Leicestershire offering top quality Prestige and Sports Cars to customers in Leicester and the surrounding areas of Loughborough, Ashby de la Zouch, Hinckley, Market Harborough and beyond.</p>\r\n<p>We are proud to offer you a first class customer service and very competitive pricing, so please browse our current stock in our online used car showroom. Here at Braunstone Crossroads Motor Company we stock a range of used cars to suit all budgets and lifestyles so we are sure to have the right used car for you.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Here''s what we offer at Braunstone Crossroads Motors</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Fantastic choice of quality used cars for sale</li>\r\n<li>Excellent value for money</li>\r\n<li>Competitive rate options on used car finance</li>\r\n<li>On-site MOT test centre</li>\r\n<li>Excellent car service and repair facilities</li>\r\n<li>Good, honest advice</li>\r\n<li>Friendly knowledgeable sales staff</li>\r\n<li>Professional level of service</li>\r\n<li>No hassle sales approach</li>\r\n<li>Established, local independent dealer</li>\r\n</ul>', NULL, '1-3 Hinkley Road, Forest East, Leicester. Leicestershire. LE3 3GL', 'With up to 100 vehicles available we are certain that we''ll have the right used car for you.', '01162390347', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439540261, 1441613930, 'https://www.facebook.com/pages/Braunstone-Crossroads-Motors/151097768375384', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'braunstone-crossroads-motors', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30451, 501179, 'http://www.parklakecars.co.uk/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>Welcome to Park Lake Cars, located in Cottenhams, Blindley Heath! If you are looking for low cost and great quality motors you have come to the right place! At Park Lake Cars we have affordable and reliable cars to suit everyone&rsquo;s budget, starting at &pound;595 to &pound;2000. We have a great selection to choose from, with over 40 cars in stock! What''s more, every car comes with an up to date MOT and warranty for your peace of mind. So if you are looking for great quality, affordability and a car dealership you can trust in the Sussex, Surry, Eastbourne and Worthing areas come to Park Lake Cars- you won&rsquo;t be disappointed!</p>', NULL, 'Cottenhams Blindley Heath Surrey RH7 6JJ', 'Car Dealership Surrey', '01342602938', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439886886, 1441270380, 'https://www.facebook.com/pages/Park-Lake-Cars/398486886982595', NULL, 'https://twitter.com/parklakecars', NULL, NULL, 'park-lake-cars', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30457, 501185, 'www.peartreevansales.co.uk', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>We are open seven days a week, all customers are welcome to visit our site at a time convenient to them. All enquiries can be made via the telephone or by sending us an email.<br /><br />All vehicles are fully valeted, HPI checked and have a pre-delivery inspection prior to sale.<br /><br />Peartree Vans site is situated between the East Sussex National Golf Course and the small rural village of Halland just off the A22.&nbsp;<br /><br />Low deposit finance available.&nbsp;We are happy to arrange finance options subject to terms &amp; conditions. We can now offer VAT deferal deposit - ring for details.&nbsp;Mainly with FSH - P/X warranties finance from 5% subject to status.</p>', NULL, 'Peartree Motors, Eastbourne Road. Near Uckfield. East Sussex. TN22 5QW', 'Peartree Vans commenced trading in the year 2000. It is a small family run business offering a professional and friendly service.', '01825841216', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439889033, 1441270511, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'peartree-motors', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30413, 501130, 'http://www.pevenseybaycarcentre.com/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>Pevensey Bay Car Centre has been selling used cars since 1983 from its unique location situated on the Sussex coast on the outskirts of sunny Eastbourne. <br /><br />We are a family business and proud of our reputation selling vehicles to our customers for over 30 years from this location. Not only do we sell and part exchange but we purchase from the general public with a ''no nonsense'' approach which means you get a valuation and a guarantee of payment within 2 hours direct to your account.<br /><br />Due to the holiday location motorhomes have become an integral part of the business and are sold throughout the year. <br /><br />We are open 7 days a week and offer finance facilities from leading lenders and of course are approved by the FCA (Financial Conduct Authority) and fully backed warranties for peace of mind motoring.<br /><br />So the next time you are looking for a car or want to sell yours why not give us a call, you''re always welcome.</p>', NULL, 'Pevensey Bay Car Centre Eastbourne Road Pevensey Bay East Sussex BN24 6HN', 'Welcome to Pevensey Bay Car Centre', '01323768844', '01323769922', NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439539891, 1440493155, 'https://www.facebook.com/pages/Pevensey-Bay-Car-Centre/169859909695744', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'pevensey-bay-car-centre', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30477, 501209, 'http://www.amavans.co.uk', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>We offer a wide range of used vehicles and all at competitive prices. If you are looking for a second hand van in the Essex &amp; Suffolk area, give us a call; up to 120 vans in stock today!</p>\r\n<p>Customer service is very important to us and we pride ourselves on keeping our customers happy by offering a helpful friendly service and answering all of your questions with a smile. If you have any questions relating to our vans and services, call us today to find out how we can help you find your next second hand van. We always aim to exceed customer expectations, offering a wide choice of used vans available in &amp; around the Essex &amp; Suffolk area, all at competitive prices.</p>\r\n<p>At Amavans we are renowned for providing premium used vans at outstanding prices. Many of the customers who have bought vans from us in the past return to buy their next used vehicle as our dealership service is second to none. Our team are experienced, trustworthy and professional - our aim is to offer you the very best value for money on used vans in North Essex.</p>\r\n<p>Our stock changes on a daily basis, so if you can''t see what you are looking for on our website then please contact us. We don''t want you to avoid missing out on our great deals. You can contact us by phone, email or by simply dropping into our showroom.</p>', NULL, 'Unit 2 - 4 Oyster Business Park , Woodrolfe Road Tollesbury Maldon Essex CM9 8SE', 'Welcome to Amavans, we are a leading used van dealer in North Essex.', '01621868374', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1440062444, 1441615518, 'http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=http://www.amavans.co.uk/', 'http://plus.google.com/share?url=http://www.amavans.co.uk/', 'http://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=http://www.amavans.co.uk/', NULL, NULL, 'amavans-ltd', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30373, 501068, 'http://www.ferry-cars.co.uk/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>We are a friendly family run business established in Newhaven since 1995. Our commitment to our customers is to provide the highest level of service, selling carefully chosen used cars prepared to the highest standard. Most cars sold come with a new MOT certificate serviced as required to include timing belt change if necessary.</p>\r\n<p>We can offer a range of financing options, subject to status, from established lenders. We can also arrange for your car to be serviced during your ownership including any diagnostic work. Don&rsquo;t hesitate to give us a call or pop down for a friendly chat.</p>', NULL, 'Railway Road, Newhaven, East Sussex, BN9 0AY', 'Ferry Car Sales - Quality used cars at prices you can afford', '01273434343', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439195212, 1440575235, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'ferry-car-sales', 'uploads/usersite/30301_30400', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30404, 501113, 'http://www.rvs4vans.co.uk/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>RVS will endeavour to find you the right van for the job. We offer a friendly and relaxed approach to sales, ensuring a worthwhile experience when choosing your vehicle.</p>\r\n<p>There''s NO VAT to pay on nearly all of our vehicles, with comprehensive warranties included as standard.</p>', NULL, 'Birch Road, Eastbourne, East Sussex, BN23 6PD', 'Welcome to RVS 4 Vans. An Established supplier of Commercial Vans and Trucks in\r\nEastbourne, East Sussex for over 20 years.', '01323810384', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439455687, 1440148345, 'https://www.facebook.com/rvs4vans', 'https://plus.google.com/104176273649643580965/about?hl=en', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'rvs-4-vans', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30378, 501073, 'http://www.affordablecarsofkent.co.uk/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>Affordable Cars of Kent is a privately run family business of used car dealers, with over 18 years experience within the motor trade. We have a wide range of used cars for sale to suit everybody, from small economical cars to family MPV''s and just about every model in between. We here at Affordable Cars of Kent, pride ourselves on our excellent level of customer service and will endeavour to meet the needs and requirements of all our customers.</p>\r\n<p>Our cars are prepared to an extremely high standard, not to be confused with your usual stock this is important to bear in mind when comparing cars.</p>\r\n<p>We are situated in the Medway town of Rochester in Kent, and are easily accessible being approximately 20 minutes from the M25 Dartford Tunnel, 15 minutes From Bluewater Shopping Centre, 15 minutes from the M20 and just five minutes from the M2.</p>\r\n<p>Our used cars for sale range from nearly new delivery mileage up to ten years of age.</p>\r\n<p>Our selection consists of mainly privately owned one owner cars with full service history. All our vehicles are sourced solely by the owner of the company to ensure they are of the highest quality. We believe this to be the reason why the majority of our customers are repeat clientele and would happily recommend us to friends and family looking for used car dealers in the area.</p>', NULL, 'Unit 28, Castleview Business Centre, Gas House Road, Rochester, Kent, ME1 1PB', 'Welcome to Affordable Cars of Kent', '01634799224', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439197027, 1440147980, 'https://www.facebook.com/pages/Affordable-Cars-Of-Kent/263421516374?ref=hl', 'https://plus.google.com/u/0/100576517522334043066/posts', 'https://twitter.com/AffordableCarsK', NULL, NULL, 'affordable-cars-of-kent', 'uploads/usersite/30301_30400', NULL, 0, NULL),
