(30428, 501150, 'www.carringtonsofhassocks.co.uk', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>We only deal in the best cars with service history as we regard our sales cars as a representation of our reputation.<br /><br />Our sales environment is one that offers a relaxed and informal atmosphere which we believe makes the process an enjoyable one that will make you want to come back again and again.<br />Our showroom is set in the picturesque village of Keymer lying at the foot of the South Downs. Easy access from major roads and Hassocks train station.<br /><br />Carringtons are always keen buyers of the very best cars with service history. Please click here and tell us all about your car that you could like to sell.<br /><br />We hope you enjoy viewing our beautifully prepared cars on our website, we look forward to meeting you soon.</p>', NULL, '68 Lewes Road, Ditchling. East Sussex. BN6 8TY', 'As a family business we have been motor dealing since the 1950''s in the Brighton area.', '01273844433', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439799161, 1441269818, 'https://www.facebook.com/pages/Carringtons-of-Hassocks/237136433019586', NULL, 'https://twitter.com/Carringtons_', NULL, NULL, 'carringtons-of-hassocks', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30401, 501110, 'http://www.danharford.co.uk/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>At Dan Harford, you can discover your next Vauxhall among our diverse selection of new models and quality Approved Used vehicles. From the Vauxhall Agila supermini to the cavernous Vauxhall Movano van, our range has something suitable for your needs and your tastes. As part of Vauxhall''s nationwide network of dealerships, we''re always among the first to receive the latest releases, meaning you could soon be enjoying the newest and most advanced models in the manufacturer''s repertoire.</p>\r\n<p>Following your purchase, our highly-skilled aftersales team will be on hand to assist you with the most advanced vehicle repair and maintenance technology, along with genuine manufacturer parts. From regular servicing and MOTs to extensive accident repairs, our master technicians can be trusted to keep your Vauxhall in peak condition.</p>\r\n<p>As a representative of Vauxhall, we are committed to upholding the superb reputation of the manufacturer, and aim to exceed customer expectations through a truly personalised service. Whether you are a single individual seeking the ideal supermini or sportscar, the head of a family looking for a spacious estate or MPV, or a business customer looking to upgrade your fleet, you can be sure that Dan Harford can support your demands. We are also proud to be part of the Motability Scheme, supplying a varied assortment of specially adapted vehicles to people with disabilities.</p>\r\n<p>We have built a solid customer base over the years at Dan Harford and, by providing on-going benefits such as Vauxhall Rewards and Vauxhall Service Club, it''s easy to see why. Explore our entire stock of vehicles online today, and don''t hesitate make an enquiry.</p>\r\n<p>For full details on our range of services and all other information, please contact us directly through one of our online contact forms.</p>', NULL, 'High Street, Kingswood, North Somerset, BS15 4AJ', 'Welcome to Dan Harford', '01172959732', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439454468, 1440148220, 'https://www.facebook.com/DanHarfordVauxhall', 'https://plus.google.com/117512968390701128994/about?hl=en', 'https://twitter.com/DanHarfordVauxh/?lang=en', NULL, NULL, 'dan-harford', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30475, 501207, 'http://www.dinnages.co.uk/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>You will find your local Dinnages car dealership in East and West Sussex conveniently located in Worthing, Haywards Heath, Burgess Hill and Brighton, where we offer a wide range of unbeatable car deals.<br /> <br /> At Dinnages, we offer the entire range of new Ford cars, new commercial vehicles, new Volvo cars and a selection of high quality used cars in Sussex, all at unbeatable prices. Our selection of Ford offers and Volvo offers are updated regularly to offer you fantastic savings across our range of new and used cars, as well as servicing and aftersales in Sussex. Take a look at our offers pages for the latest deals available and contact us for further information.</p>', NULL, NULL, 'Dinnages Car Dealers in Sussex are proud to represent Ford, Ford Commercial, Renault and Volvo across the county.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1440061408, 1441614760, 'https://www.facebook.com/pages/Dinnages-Worthing-Haywards-Heath-Burgess-Hill-Brighton/10666269273235', NULL, 'https://twitter.com/DinnagesGarages', NULL, NULL, 'dinnages', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30398, 501104, 'http://www.garageonthegreen.com', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>We are pleased to always have on for sale between 40 and 50 quality used cars based in St Leonards on Sea near Hastings for you to look at at your leisure.</p>\r\n<p>We have been in business for over 20 years and in that time we have built up many friendly contacts in the local motor trade enabling us to source quality used cars at the best prices. If you know the car you want and we don&rsquo;t have it in stock we&rsquo;ll aim to source it for you.</p>\r\n<p>Many of our customers, both local and national return to us again and again as they are impressed with the level of service received and they often recommend us to friends and family.</p>\r\n<p>Your current car can be used as full deposit on any one of our quality used cars and a finance deal, if required, can be tailored to suit every pocket.</p>\r\n<p>Your new car will come &lsquo;as standard&rsquo; with a full HPI check, new MOT, 6 month warranty, with options to extend for up to three years at an additional cost, and a service as required.</p>', NULL, NULL, 'If you are looking for the best second hand cars for sale in St Leonards on Sea and Hastings in East Sussex, you have come to the right place!', '01424718080', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439369876, 1441371905, 'https://www.facebook.com/GarageOnTheGreen', NULL, 'https://twitter.com/GarageGreen', NULL, NULL, 'garage-on-the-green', 'uploads/usersite/30301_30400', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30431, 501153, 'http://www.gmacommercials.com/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>We are an established truck and van centre near Eastbourne with over 19 years experience.We supply a range of new &amp; used vehicles at very affordable prices &amp; specialise in 1 owner vehicles.<br /><br />We are situated along the A22 at Lower Dicker adjacent to the willow cafe and are just 1 mile from the main town of Hailsham which has main line train stations nearby where we provide transport to &amp; from for customers.We are within an hours drive from London and just a short drive from anywhere in Kent, Sussex and Surrey.We also have a site atSwanley Kent 1 mile from Jct 3 M25 where we stock a range of 12ton+ HGV''s.<br /><br />Our experienced sales team give good advise to help choose the right vehicle for you.We have a selection of finance options in place to get you the best deal.We can also arrange delivery of your commercial vehicle to anywhere within the UK and make regular deliveries to all major ports for export.We pride ourselves on our good quality service and good quality commercials which make GMA Commercials the only choice to make.</p>', NULL, 'GMA Commercials A22 Lower Dicker  Hailsham East Sussex BN27 4BT', 'Welcome to GMA Commercials, Used Van and Truck Dealer in Hailsham near Eastbourne East Sussex.', '01323441090', '07831104419', NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439799724, 1440490993, 'https://www.facebook.com/GMACommercials?sk=app_175456335854933', 'https://plus.google.com/104084479951623441557/about?hl=en', 'https://twitter.com/GMACOMMERCIALS', NULL, NULL, 'gma-commercials', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
