(30484, 501216, 'http://www.v12sportsandclassics.co.uk/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>At V12 Sports &amp; Classics Ltd we like to keep our customers happy by offering an excellent personal service. We have a great selection of used cars to suit every need and budget.</p>\r\n<p>We have vast experience and knowledge in a huge variety of used cars. For great deals V12 Sports &amp; Classics Ltd will have a car to suit all your needs at a price you&rsquo;ll love!</p>', NULL, 'Unit 23, Harrow Brook Industrial Estate, Leicestershire, Hinckley, LE10 3DJ', 'Welcome to V12 Sports and Classics. The cheapest cars in the UK from Leicesters premier Car Supermarket.', '01455560078', '07947561482', NULL, NULL, NULL, 1440065975, 1440148422, 'https://www.facebook.com/V12SportsAndClassics', 'https://plus.google.com/105619312689270457923/posts?hl=en', 'https://twitter.com/V12SC', NULL, NULL, 'v12-sports-classics-ltd', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30447, 501171, 'www.vanwisegroup.com', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>Since 2003, through our Van Sales, Van Hire and Servicing departments, we have provided quality vehicles at the most competitive prices to thousands of satisfied customers. Our purchasing policy ensures that we acquire vehicles at the most advantageous prices which enables us to pass the savings on to our customers. &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>When purchasing a vehicle Vanwise is able to provide a comprehensive set of services to make ownership of the vehicle as simple and easy as possible. &nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>To purchase the vehicle we can arrange financing including a non deposit facility.</li>\r\n<li>For peace of mind we include a free HPI check on your vehicle and offer extended warranty periods if required.</li>\r\n<li>We ensure excellent quality upon taking delivery by carrying out a full valet of your vehicle and completing a thorough pre-delivery inspection.</li>\r\n<li>Throughout the ownership of your vehicle Vanwise can provide a one stop shop for all your servicing, maintenance and MOT testing needs.</li>\r\n<li>When hiring a vehicle Vanwise offers a package of flexible hiring alternatives. From multi vehicle fleet contracts, with the associated comprehensive account management, to vehicle hire on a daily, weekly, weekend or longer term basis.</li>\r\n</ul>', NULL, 'Vanwise Group, Bircholt Road, Maidstone. Kent. ME15 9XY', 'Welcome to Vanwise Essex - Used Vans in Essex and Kent.', '01279457562', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439804517, 1441270601, NULL, 'https://plus.google.com/103165195500091355135/?hl=en', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'vanwise-group', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30446, 501170, 'http://www.voitureltd.co.uk/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>Voiture are located on the A269 in the high street, Sidley, Bexhill-on-Sea, East Sussex, adjacent to Lidl supermarket. Complete with two onsite workshops we offer a wide range of low mileage pre-owned cars, full servicing and mechanical facilities, specializing in the Suzuki, Saab and Vauxhall marques with ample customer parking nearby.</p>', NULL, 'Voiture Ltd, 76 Ninfield Road, Sidley, Bexhill-on-Sea, East Sussex. TN39 5BB', 'Car Sales and Service Centre', '01424730750', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439803900, 1441613429, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'voiture-ltd', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30468, 501200, 'http://www.classicautomobiles.co.uk/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>At Classic Automobiles we are dedicated to providing our customers with the best vehicles, service and support. Our staff are always available to assist with your needs and we are committed to your satisfaction.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>For over 35 years we have gained a reputation for supplying quality cars at very competitive prices, presented to the very highest standards.</p>', NULL, 'Classic Automobiles, 78-81 Morland Road, Croydon, Surrey, CR0 6HA', 'Classic Automobiles, great deals on used cars in Croydon', '02077687003', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1440059002, 1441614430, 'https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=http://www.classicautomobiles.co.uk', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'classic-automobiles-croydon', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
