(49558, 502431, 'http://shabitattrevived.co.uk/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>Here at Shabitatt we buy and sell furniture:<br />Shabitatt Revived sells items we have up-cycled ourselves such as hand-painted furniture and our fabulous desks / console tables made using reclaimed Singer sewing machine bases and pine planks.</p>\r\n<p>Shabitatt To Shabbychic is where we sell items of furniture not yet up-cycled, to customers who may wish to keep it original or up-cycle the item themselves.<br />We don''t sell paint- this is so we aren''t limitied to one particular brand. We particularly love using both Annie Sloan and Frenchic chalk paints, but also like to paint some items using Farrow &amp; Ball eggshell paints</p>', NULL, NULL, 'Furniture - Vintage, antique and industrial with a little modern thrown in for good measure', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1440688901, 1440689560, 'https://www.facebook.com/ShabitattVintage', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'shabitatt', 'uploads/usersite/49501_49600', NULL, 0, NULL);
