(30403, 501112, 'http://www.scs4vans.com/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>Our experienced sales team has extensive product knowledge what will help you find the corect vehicle for the job, they can talk you firstly through selecting the right vehicle for the job and then advise you through every aspect of buying your new vehicle; this if you wish can all be done before you even visit our garage, making your visit to SCS the only one you need to make!!</p>', NULL, 'Lewes Road, Wilmington, Eastbourne East Sussex, BN26 5SG', 'South coasts leading used van dealership', '01323484811', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439455156, 1440492929, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'scs4vans', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30391, 501098, 'http://www.westerhamgarage.co.uk/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>Welcome to Westerham Garage, the complete service. Westerham Garage is still a local family run garage, offering a complete service with a close and friendly working relationship with all our customers. <br /><br />Formerly Wolfe Garage, we have been associated with the Volkswagen Group since 1955, with SEAT joining us back in 1993. <br /><br />Whatever you require our fully trained technicians and long serving staff will offer full dealership facilities and more. If it is fitted to a vehicle, from tyre to roof rack, from headlamp bulb to tow bar, we are involved.<br /><br />Offering used cars to Westerham, Sevenoaks, Croydon, Bromley, Kent, Surrey and Sussex.</p>', NULL, 'Westerham Garage London Road Westerham Kent TN16 2DJ', 'Welcome to Westerham Garage, used car dealer in Westerham, Kent.', '08452575400', '01959564906', NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439368222, 1440147124, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'westerham-garage', 'uploads/usersite/30301_30400', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30456, 501184, 'www.spurofslindon.co.uk', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>We pride ourselves on our customer care and after sale service resulting in a large proportion of repeat business and word of mouth advertising.</p>\r\n<p>We always carry a stock of at least 50 carefully chosen vans which are bought from reputable sources including BT, lease companies, manufacturers and main dealers. The vans are of all sizes including&nbsp;LWB&rsquo;s, pickups, tipper, dropsides and 4 X 4&rsquo;s. Whilst specialising inFords&nbsp;(many direct from BT), we also stock a selection of&nbsp;Vauxhalls, Toyotas, Nissans, Peugeots, Citroens and Volkswagens. All the vans are fully serviced and valeted to the highest standards and include a comprehensive warranty.<br /><br />Our experienced staff are always on hand to offer expert advice on which van best suits your requirements. They can also arrange sign writing, towing equipment, specialist bodies, ply lining and additional seating if needed. If any vehicle you request is not currently in stock, they will try to find it for you.</p>\r\n<p>See the All Stock section for full listings of our current stock.&nbsp;<br /><br />We offer full finance and leasing facilities and take all major credit cards.<br /><br />For all enquiries, please contact us on telephone number&nbsp;01243 814651</p>', NULL, 'Spur of Slindon, London Road, Slindon Common. Arundel. West Sussex. BN18 0NE', 'Spur Vans of Slindon is a family run business established in 1994 specialising in the sale of competitively priced, high quality used vans.', '01243814651', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439888503, 1441270627, 'https://www.facebook.com/pages/Spur-Garage-Ltd/377901735632666', 'https://plus.google.com/106853030563241136615/about?hl=en', 'https://twitter.com/SpurGarageLtd', NULL, NULL, 'spur-of-slindon', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30440, 501162, 'http://www.vfmautosales.co.uk', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>With 29 Years Experience in the Motor Trade Stewart Arthur at VFM Autosales Ltd strives to provide the best quality Used Cars at the most competitive prices.Our policy is geared towards Customer Retention so our Service before and after Sale is Top Notch.We have on Site Preparation including an MOT Station,Fully Equipped Workshop with Up to date Diagnostics,Highly Experienced Technicians,Are Air Conditioning Specialists and offer Free Loan Cars.Try us for your next Secondhand Car,I am certain you will enjoy the experience.</p>', NULL, 'VFM Auto Sales, Groombridge Garage, Withyham Road. Groombridge. Kent. TN3 9QW', 'Welcome to Vfm Auto Sales. Quality Used Cars from Stewart Arthur.', '01892861416', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439802058, 1441615227, NULL, 'https://plus.google.com/103398801733342875947/about?hl=en', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'vfm-auto-sales', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30480, 501212, 'http://www.carsandtyreskent.co.uk/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>f you are looking for affordable tyres or to buy a second hand car in Kent, then visit Cars and Tyres Kent located in Ashford where you are guaranteed to find a fantastic selection of cars and tyres for sale.<br /><br />Cars and Tyres Kent has a great reputation and is well known in Ashford for its quality used second hand cars at very competitive prices. We also offer a fantastic after sales service, providing repairs &amp; servicing for all makes of cars, are scrap metal merchants and use the latest technology in Diagnostic Equipment. <br /><br />Our other specialism besides sales is car tyres so if you''re looking for a particular set of tyres for your vehicle at an affordable price then please give us a call, we are open 7 days a week.<br /><br />If you would like to come and visit our Ashford showroom or arrange a test drive on a particular car please complete the enquiry form and one of our dedicated team will contact you to arrange a time that suits you.<br /><br />Alternatively don''t hesitate to call us now on 01233 238262</p>', NULL, 'Kingsnorth Iron Works, Ashford Road Kingsnorth Ashford Kent TN26 1NJ', 'Car Tyres Kent, Cars and Tyres Kent, Car Dealer Ashford', '01233238262', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1440063522, 1441184083, 'http://www.facebook.com/pages/Affordable-Car-Co/464726536899242', NULL, 'https://twitter.com/AffordableCarCo', NULL, NULL, 'cars-and-tyres-kent', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30399, 501105, 'http://www.sussextradecentres.co.uk', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>Our two outlets are both a couple of minutes drive from the A22/A27 Polegate Bypass on the outskirts of Eastbourne at Stone Cross and Westham/Pevensey.<br /><br />Both branches operate in conjunction with the RAC and specialise in offering only very low mileage, superior quality used vehicles from &pound;2,000-&pound;10,000.<br /><br />Sussex Trade Centres are pleased to offer over 150 affordable cars to choose from together with personalised finance options and generous part-exchange allowances.</p>', NULL, 'Sussex Trade Centres Rattle Road (A4260) Stone Cross Eastbourne East Sussex BN24 5EB', 'Welcome to Sussex Trade Centres, a family run business, selling used cars in the Eastbourne area for over 30 years.', '01323461666', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439370146, 1441183019, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'sussex-trade-centres-ltd', 'uploads/usersite/30301_30400', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30435, 501157, 'www.central-cs.co.uk', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>Central Car Sales is based in Bexhill East Sussex and is the longest established car showroom in the area. Central was started up in 1991 by the present owner of the company Stephen White who was born in the local area. <br /><br />The site holds fame to being a Volvo and Vauxhall dealer ship in the 60s and next door to The Elva sports racing car production in the 50s. As local people are aware, Bexhill was the birth place of British motor racing.<br /><br />Here at Central Car Sales Steve has selected only the quality and best value and after sales service that you would expect from as he worked for main dealers such as Toyota, Ford, Citroen and Honda dealer ships.</p>', NULL, 'Central Car Sales Bexhill, 94 London Road. Bexhill. East Sussex. TN39 3LE', 'Welcome to Central Car Sales of Bexhill. We specialise in all types of used cars including BMW, Mercedes Benz and Audi.', '01424734859', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439800359, 1441269668, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'central-car-sales-bexhill', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30442, 501164, 'http://www.target-cars.co.uk/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>Target Cars is a family run RAC dealer established in 1999, which prides its self in selling a good selection of quality used cars at realistic prices.</p>\r\n<p>Our online car sales showroom features a wide variety of low mileage second hand cars with multiple photos to give you a reliable and complete picture for all of our used cars!</p>', NULL, 'Springwell Road, Beare Green  Dorking  Surrey  RH5 4RN', 'Welcome to Target Cars\r\nQuality used cars for Sale in Dorking, Surrey', '01306711457', '07786167749', NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439802540, 1441614116, 'https://www.facebook.com/pages/Target-Cars/118702584905870', NULL, 'https://twitter.com/@targetcars', NULL, NULL, 'target-cars', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
